<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body{
            background-color:lightskyblue;
            position:absolute;
            width:100%;
            height:100vh;
        }
        .box{
            width:30%;
            height:fit-content;
            padding:1rem;
            background-color:rgba(55, 60, 107, 0.733);
            border-radius:1rem;
            color:white;
            position:relative;
            top:50%;
            left:50%;
            transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
            justify-content:center;
            align-items:center;
        }
        button{
            padding:0.5rem;
            color:white;
            background-color:cornflowerblue;
        }
        input{
            padding:0.3rem;
            color:black;
            border-radius:0.1rem;
        }
    </style>
    <title>채팅방 입장하기</title>
</head>
<body>
    <form class="box" method="post" action="/chat">
        <label for="name">채팅 시 사용할 이름을 입력해 주세요</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" required autofocus>
        <button type="submit">입장</button>
    </form>
</body>
